PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of MANMEET BHATIA of Vancouver, British-Columbia, to be a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the Canadian Museum of History, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Laurier Turgeon, whose term has expired.
